        <item>
            <title>iPhone 16 发布会邀请函证实造假　制作者自爆是用 AI 生成图片的恶作剧</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/22/iphone16-apple-event-invite-is-fake/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=iphone16-apple-event-invite-is-fake</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/22/iphone16-apple-event-invite-is-fake/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Ngan Ivan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 05:08:03 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[城中热话]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提电话]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[社交网络]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iPhone 16]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1257773</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">知名 Apple 爆料用户 <a href="https://x.com/MajinBuOfficial">@MajinBuOfficial</a> 早前在 X 平台上分享他收到了疑似是 Apple iPhone 16 发布会的邀请函，从邀请函中得知活动将于太平洋时间 9 月 10 日上午 10 时（即香港时间 9 月 11 日凌晨 1 时）举行。最新消息为邀请函已经被证实造假，单纯是一场对爆料用户的恶作剧。</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">According to what I was told by a source who asked to remain anonymous, the new Apple event where the iPhone 16 will be presented, will be held on September 10 2024. <br />This should be the cover of the invitation <a href="https://t.co/7jGoafHaOU">pic.twitter.com/7jGoafHaOU</a></p><p>&mdash; Majin Bu (@MajinBuOfficial) <a href="https://twitter.com/MajinBuOfficial/status/1825466723023139243?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">August 19, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">Fun fact: i made the &quot;leaked&quot; Apple Event invite in less than 10 minutes using figma and an Ai generated texture   <br />and i sent it to the leaker just because i was bored <a href="https://t.co/3tX9QgUy4p">pic.twitter.com/3tX9QgUy4p</a></p><p>&mdash; Lore (@lorevfx) <a href="https://twitter.com/lorevfx/status/1825815959166189789?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">August 20, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p style="font-weight: 400;">X 用户 <a href="https://x.com/lorevfx">@lorevfx</a> 将自己制作这个假的 iPhone 16 发布会邀请函的整个过程上传，并表示自己使用免费的线上设计工具 Figma 和 AI 工具辅助，仅花了不足 10 分钟便完成整个伪造的邀请函。至于制作这个恶作剧的原因，他表示单纯是出于无聊。</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="zxx" dir="ltr"><a href="https://t.co/DYuPXLyuDc">pic.twitter.com/DYuPXLyuDc</a></p><p>&mdash; Lore (@lorevfx) <a href="https://twitter.com/lorevfx/status/1825915465677324521?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">August 20, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p>Lore 将当初与 Majin Bu 的聊天记录上传，并表示自己用一个愚蠢的故事就成功说服了 Majin Bu 将这个假的邀请函发布。邀请函被证实造假之后，Majin Bu 并没有因为被欺骗而感到生气，反而十分欣赏他的付出甚至将伪造的邀请函制成了桌布。网民直指 Lore 是天才，不过都有网民认为现时的爆料用户不负责任，完全不理会资料的真确性就将其发布。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">资料来源：<a href="https://www.cultofmac.com/news/iphone-16-event-invite-leaks-september-2024?fbclid=IwY2xjawEzlcJleHRuA2FlbQIxMAABHV1eGIQhpOGJhbGZfeDUqy6K5bH419byCRInqTSABpCwS9-Yn9mvnK_F8A_aem_YAltz9zXqwfxJck0YwIR6w">Cult of Mac</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/01/apple-intelligence-7-functions/tips-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教学+实试】Apple Intelligence 7 大实用功能　一键校对英文文法 + TLDR 长文总结 + 录音即时转文字</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/01/iphone-clear-cache-2024/tips-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教学】帮 iPhone 清除 IG、FB 无用垃圾　实试释放手机 16 GB 储存容量</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/30/ios-18-1-beta-apple-inteligence/tips-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教学】香港都可用 Apple Intelligence　安装方法 + 申请教学</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/22/iphone16-apple-event-invite-is-fake/mobile-phone/">iPhone 16 发布会邀请函证实造假　制作者自爆是用 AI 生成图片的恶作剧</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
