        <item>
            <title>【评测】模寿 x BLITZWAY 真三一万能侠　LED 灯效惊艳 + 跳齿式关节</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/22/moshowtoysblitzwaygetter/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=moshowtoysblitzwaygetter</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/22/moshowtoysblitzwaygetter/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Gary Lee]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 04:30:48 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[玩具]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1256633</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>近年来，真三一万能侠合金 Figure 大家都见得多了，多厂也相继有推出各自有独特风格的版本，而今次最新推出的是由模寿与 BLITZWAY 合作，真三一万能侠合金 Figure，售价为人民币$980，折合约港币$1,100 左右，确实引起了不少关注，而这个版本又有什么特点呢？小编已收到送测版本，立即为大家开箱。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257712" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_0644-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_0644-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_0644-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">当然又是大大盒的了。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257713" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_0643-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_0643-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_0643-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">极具份量，整箱重 5.2KG。</p><p>外观设计方面，这款真三一万能侠相当忠于原作。最为人瞩目的是其标志性的「水桶腰」造型，线条简洁有力。表面采用高光泽度处理，尤其是红色部分，呈现出类似跑车烤漆的质感，视觉效果十分抢眼。然而，这种处理也带来了一些小问题，如容易留下指纹，需要经常擦拭保养。头部设计亦相当出色，不仅还原了真三一万能侠锐利的眼神，还提供了多种可替换的表情部件，虽然效果不是特别明显，但也体现了制作团队的用心。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257714" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0303-694x510.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="510" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0303-694x510.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0303-scaled.jpg 1226w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257715" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0356-694x407.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="407" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0356-694x407.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0356-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><a title="_DSC0318" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53938406694/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53938406694_2d58069163_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0318" width="1024" height="688" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC0327" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53938323858/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53938323858_304de9c8e8_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0327" width="1024" height="601" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC0319" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53938073516/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53938073516_04cfd7b039_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0319" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257717" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0322-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0322-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0322-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257718" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0323-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0323-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0323-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257720" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0325-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0325-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0325-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257722" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0313-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0313-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0313-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257723" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0314-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0314-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0314-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>灯光效果是这部真三一万能侠的一大特色。头部、胸口、腰部和手臂等多个部位都配备了 LED 灯组，可说是全身都可亮齐灯光效果，电池方面就要用到 AG1 及 AG13 电池，每种需要 8 粒。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257724" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0307-694x455.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="455" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0307-694x455.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0307-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257725" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0310-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0310-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0310-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257726" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0311-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0311-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0311-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>由于今次是测试版，尚有地方会再作改良，例如手腕装 LED 位置的扣位，会有扣不稳的情况掉下，厂方说到时真正出货时这方面会作出改良；现时的卡扣设是想可以让用家容易点换电，但又要卡得到可负担到重型武器两把大斧的重量。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257739" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0309-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0309-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0309-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><a title="_DSC0412" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53938323688/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53938323688_86b1f82b9b_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0412" width="1024" height="624" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>其中，胸口和腿部的灯光效果表现优秀，亮度充足，光线分布均匀。然而，头部和手臂的灯光效果则稍显逊色。真三一还附带了一些特效配件，如可发光的烈阳闪光弹，增加了摆 pose 的趣味性。</p><p><a title="_DSC0334" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53938528675/in/dateposted-public/" 