oading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257731" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0350-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0350-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0350-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257732" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0351-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0351-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0351-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>可动性方面，这部真三一表现达到中上程度。虽然某些部位的活动范围有限，但整体来说足以应对大多数常见 Pose。值得一赞的是，真三一万能侠大量采用了齿轮结构，大大提升了关节的稳定性，带来了极佳的把玩手感，小编就特别喜爱这种跳齿式关节了。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257719" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0324-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0324-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0324-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257721" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0328-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0328-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0328-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>配件方面，真三一配备了多种配件，包括标志性的真三一战斧和真三一镰刀。这些武器尺寸夸张，造型霸气，能够有效增强真三一的视觉冲击力。另一个值得一提的配件是重达 2 公斤的展示地台，地台采用了动画中 Invader 的造型，增加了展示效果。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257734" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0352-694x337.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="337" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0352-694x337.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0352-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257735" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0354-694x358.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="358" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0354-694x358.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0354-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257736" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0355-694x360.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="360" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0355-694x360.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0355-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257737" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0420-694x486.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="486" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0420-694x486.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0420-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257738" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0421-694x429.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="429" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0421-694x429.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0421-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>Action Pose</h2><p><a title="_DSC0386 (1)" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53938073351/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53938073351_898b539fa0_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0386 (1)" width="1024" height="623" /></a></p><p><a title="_DSC0361" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53938323738/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53938323738_fa764d4e3d_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0361" width="966" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC0408" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53938406619/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53938406619_a65da83f4f_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0408" width="848" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC0372" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53937169757/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53937169757_1e86d35c68_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0372" width="1024" height="650" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script>这款模寿与 BLITZWAY 合作的真三一万能侠是一个有潜力的作品，它在造型设计、部分灯光效果和稳定性等方面表现出色，为真三一万能侠爱好者提供了一个不错的选择。而大约 HK$1,1xx 的定价，可说是高性价比了。不过，如果能够简化地台以降低价格，可能更能提升吸引力。</p><p><a title="_DSC0340" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53937169737/i